  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Honey Bee With Guns</strong>, as a bee, your mission is to fly from flower to flower, collecting nectar to turn it into honey. But be careful, enemy bees are out there, ready to sabotage your honey production and steal your precious nectar (or even your queen)! Moreover, a mysterious fungus is spreading, turning innocent insects into terrifying zombies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use honey to buy your items and abilities in Grandma's shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/52656d90045591df9b3e0f4c2f5198e5.poster.avif?t=1761012268\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/52656d90045591df9b3e0f4c2f5198e5.webm?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/52656d90045591df9b3e0f4c2f5198e5.mp4?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect various flowers around the world! Some a bit tough, others made of metal, and some just strange...and discover new honeys when depositing them in the hive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/854ee7f46518bc02aee172d9057d622b.poster.avif?t=1761012268\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/854ee7f46518bc02aee172d9057d622b.webm?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/854ee7f46518bc02aee172d9057d622b.mp4?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are various elements in the environment that can be used as weapons. The more bees you have, the more elements can be modified or used to your advantage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/cefb274b1fff37e3fe2f8634155f0db9.poster.avif?t=1761012268\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/cefb274b1fff37e3fe2f8634155f0db9.webm?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/cefb274b1fff37e3fe2f8634155f0db9.mp4?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expand your hive.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more honey you have, the more you can trade for new bees or expand your hive in the Queen Bee's shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/4ce6ab1170c2abec6867c665a1c2a2f5.poster.avif?t=1761012268\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/4ce6ab1170c2abec6867c665a1c2a2f5.webm?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/4ce6ab1170c2abec6867c665a1c2a2f5.mp4?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some animals are being controlled by a mysterious force. Defeat them to survive and earn new weapons.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/4742ce9c9a0d1b46fc7284575ba13220.poster.avif?t=1761012268\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/4742ce9c9a0d1b46fc7284575ba13220.webm?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/4742ce9c9a0d1b46fc7284575ba13220.mp4?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for an epic battle against this evil fungus as you unlock new areas by exploring and completing missions to eradicate the zombie threat once and for all! So, strap on your wings, head to the gym for your daily workout, and get ready for an adventure full of challenges and, of course, delicious honey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Honey Bee With Guns</strong>, as a bee, your mission is to fly from flower to flower, collecting nectar to turn it into honey. But be careful, enemy bees are out there, ready to sabotage your honey production and steal your precious nectar (or even your queen)! Moreover, a mysterious fungus is spreading, turning innocent insects into terrifying zombies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use honey to buy your items and abilities in Grandma's shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/52656d90045591df9b3e0f4c2f5198e5.poster.avif?t=1761012268\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/52656d90045591df9b3e0f4c2f5198e5.webm?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/52656d90045591df9b3e0f4c2f5198e5.mp4?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect various flowers around the world! Some a bit tough, others made of metal, and some just strange...and discover new honeys when depositing them in the hive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/854ee7f46518bc02aee172d9057d622b.poster.avif?t=1761012268\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/854ee7f46518bc02aee172d9057d622b.webm?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/854ee7f46518bc02aee172d9057d622b.mp4?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are various elements in the environment that can be used as weapons. The more bees you have, the more elements can be modified or used to your advantage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/cefb274b1fff37e3fe2f8634155f0db9.poster.avif?t=1761012268\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/cefb274b1fff37e3fe2f8634155f0db9.webm?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/cefb274b1fff37e3fe2f8634155f0db9.mp4?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expand your hive.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more honey you have, the more you can trade for new bees or expand your hive in the Queen Bee's shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/4ce6ab1170c2abec6867c665a1c2a2f5.poster.avif?t=1761012268\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/4ce6ab1170c2abec6867c665a1c2a2f5.webm?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/4ce6ab1170c2abec6867c665a1c2a2f5.mp4?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some animals are being controlled by a mysterious force. Defeat them to survive and earn new weapons.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/4742ce9c9a0d1b46fc7284575ba13220.poster.avif?t=1761012268\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/4742ce9c9a0d1b46fc7284575ba13220.webm?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927910/extras/4742ce9c9a0d1b46fc7284575ba13220.mp4?t=1761012268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for an epic battle against this evil fungus as you unlock new areas by exploring and completing missions to eradicate the zombie threat once and for all! So, strap on your wings, head to the gym for your daily workout, and get ready for an adventure full of challenges and, of course, delicious honey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
